Class Attachment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.storage.model.Attachment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataModel

    @Entity
public class Attachment
extends Object
implements DataModel
    Store information about attachments.

    The actual bytes are written to a file on disk. See AttachmentDAO.

    Timothy Ham, Zinovii Dmytriv
